{"tid":118883,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"啱啱有囡囡跟踪我。。。。。。","createTime":"2017-02-13T10:47:05.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-13T11:10:29.000Z","uid":82007,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"5b62d6ed8e774555686e04d14712ac1789a30bf3","tid":118883,"uid":82007,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-13T10:47:05.000Z","msg":"是咁的，小弟本來毒自一人係返hall既路上，因為好凍既關係所以行得勁快，但竟然有人跟得上我快過保特既速度，一直緊貼係我身後，而係我放慢速度既同時，佢又減速，我加速果陣佢又加速。我回頭一望，發覺佢都幾靚女，呢個時候我其實已經知道咩料。<br />\n<br />\n冇錯，佢其實係比我身上一樣極具魅力既野吸引住。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n冇錯，其實係佢無帶卡所以要跟實我先入到hall<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dbae2dd2412ed9ee8003788dbef15e6db754030f","tid":118883,"uid":60861,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-13T10:57:14.000Z","msg":"樓豬小心佢有鳩"},{"pid":"70fe76f1e3a963eee1eda8417daf9896daf89b14","tid":118883,"uid":82007,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-13T11:10:29.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>樓豬小心佢有鳩</blockquote><br />\n個樣J得落就夠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n入去個陣佢仲好溫柔咁對我甜笑，<br />\n講左聲唔該"}]}